race.comment: HE'S A PEARL (7) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 2.5 lengths (29.57) at this track. The one to beat again. ZIPPING ARKLE (2) was a brilliant winner two back but last start drifted back and wound up strongly to finish a 6 length third at this track (30.56). The form out of last race has been strong. Can feature again. SEE THIS (5) clocked a swift 29.75 finishing second in a Grade 5 at this track last start. Top win latest and can measure up again. MOTOR CITY CHIEF (1) cannot be ruled out.
